  Mkhize was apprehended
   by an off-duty police officer who heard the sound of gunshots and suspected that someone had been hijacked in the 
  neighbourhood
  , he gave chase and made the arrest.
 
 
  
 
 
  A third suspect is still on the run.
 
 
  
 
 
  The case was adjourned to August 16 for further investigations.
 

 

 

